    "en": {
      "title": "16 crore liters of fuel distributed in August",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "National Fuel License or QR. The Ministry of Energy said that 16 crore liters of fuel were issued last August using the code, of which 10 crore liters of petrol and 6 crore liters of diesel were issued.",
        "He said that this fuel stock is from 1265 Cipetco and IOC filling stations and there is no fuel shortage in the country anymore."
      ],
